Text:
lol, i love your description.
Thanks, I'm gonna check this out.

I promised myself I would never do the absurdly annoying "SEEEEED" (and I hoped I would never have to ask such a thing in the first place) but now I am. This torrent has been stuck at 32.9% for the last 6 months -- and I'm kinda getting tired of waiting for it, no matter how much I want the contents. So then, if I ask quite nicely, will you please seed?
